hDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O God! Please bless me with being steadfast in my affairs, seeking counsel with those with admonition and love for me, humbleness in my heart, and asking for blessing of what You have Bestowed on me. O God! Please bless me with health of the heart and acceptance of what You Like and You Please.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ ارْزُقْنِي التَّثَبُّتَ فِيْ اَمْرِيْ وَالْمُشَاوَرَةَ مَعَ اَهْلِ النَّصِيْحَةِ وَالْمَوَدَّةِ لِيْ بِالتَّوَاضُعِ فِيْ قَلْبِيْ وَالْتِمَاسَ الْبَرَكَةِ فِيْمَا اَنْعَمْتَ بِهٖ عَلَيَّ۔ اَللّٰهُمَّ ارْزُقْنِيْ سَلَامَةَ الصَّدْرِ وَالسَّكِيْنَةَ اِلٰى مَا تُحِبُّ وَتَرْضٰى۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "Arabic